<figureCitation box="[447,597,763,790]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="3.[151,250,1974,1998]" captionTargetBox="[170,1418,632,1950]" captionTargetId="figure-257@3.[170,1418,632,1950]" captionTargetPageId="3" captionText="FIGURE 1. Adults of Phyllocnistis canta n. sp. (A–B), Phyllocnistis elongata n. sp. (C–D) and Phyllocnistis furcata Vargas &amp; Cerdeña (E–F). (A, C, E) dorsal view, (B, D, F) detail of right forewing. Scale bars: 2 mm (A, C, D, E), 1 mm (B, F)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6280737" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6280737/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="202">Figs. 1. C, D</figureCitation>
